How to attribute
----------------
Please credit the Visual Learning Lab (UC San Diego) and cite the dataset paper:

  Long, B., Fan, J. E., Huey, H., Chai, Z., & Frank, M. C. (2024). Parallel
  developmental changes in children's production and recognition of line
  drawings of visual concepts. Nature Communications.
  https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-023-44529-9


Notes
-----
The underlying drawings and behavioral data originate from the
`drawing_production_and_recognition` project (cogtoolslab); see that project for
the source data and its terms. This repository packages derived data and
interactive visualizations of it.
